《復聯3》，在最新公佈的周末票房排<br />\n行榜上，它還是屈居次位，輸給了已經第三週上映的劇場版《名偵探柯南：零之執行人》<br />\n。<br />\n<br />\n不過由於日本的影片排行榜是以觀影人次計算，《柯南》才實現了三連霸。若以票房成績<br />\n計算，《復聯3》6.72億日元票房，略超《名偵探柯南：零之執行人》的6.1億日元票房。<br />\n<br />\n觀影人次方面，《柯南》週末兩日吸引45.3萬人次觀看，《復聯3》吸引43.7萬人次。 《<br />\n復聯3》以IMAX、3D、4DX等製式上映時，票價較高，因此票房仍高於《柯南》。<br />\n<br />\n2015年7月4號日本上映的《復仇者聯盟2》首周登頂（比北美遲了2個月），首周末兩日拿<br />\n下7.939億日元票房，比《復聯3》多出1億多日元。<br />\n<br />\n2012年8月14號（週二）日本上映的《復仇者聯盟》首周同樣登頂（比北美遲了3個月），<br />\n首周末（8.18-19）兩日票房5.93億日元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/movie/M.1525274632.A.97E.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2Fmovie%2FM.1525274632.A.97E.html&d=LIBfEwBbbbuceM9MXPAJA0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=4573266a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/movie/M.1525274632.A.97E.html</a>"},{"pid":"a3fd4e09358449e1bc0889e79e10f9e43c5cea1e","tid":650702,"uid":4008,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T23:39:33.000Z","msg":"飛咗過去睇柯南<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2aeab4c643acb95148847350e4f12c4a00f9b03","tid":650702,"uid":64009,"like":16,"dislike":18,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T23:45:46.000Z","msg":"柯南好睇禁多<br />\n話婦聯好睇果班成班井底蛙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22540600d64a8bf5a46234563c4b1e739a71db0a","tid":650702,"uid":34205,"like":3,"dislike":21,"score":-18,"quote":{"pid":"8de55e090f3b255811d8af651f9fbee40782be85","tid":650702,"uid":134883,"like":23,"dislike":19,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T15:33:54.000Z","msg":"如果香港人都係咁，港產片就有救喇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T23:46:40.000Z","msg":"你瞓醒未呀？無香港電影㗎<br />\n再講，人地啲作品高過港片幾班啦"},{"pid":"7f6138c088c3554cb43f9ee7c126277cafe133de","tid":650702,"uid":95452,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57090f6833d7edef94ecaffb9af95cb8591f0249","tid":650702,"uid